sorcer.core.context
Class SharedAssociativeContext

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Dictionary<K,V>
      java.util.Hashtable<String,Object>
          sorcer.core.context.ServiceContext
              sorcer.core.context.SharedAssociativeContext
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Map, AssociativeContext, SpaceContext, SorcerConstants, Context, Evaluation, Identifiable, Revaluation
public class SharedAssociativeContext
extends ServiceContext
implements SpaceContext

SpaceContext persists its dataContext nodes in a distributed array in JavaSpace with the name provided in the constructor. In the data dataContext path values correspond to indices of elements in the distributed array.
